{{!Factory Careeers}}

{{> layout/head page-title="Factory Careers"}}

{{> layout/header }}
{{>blocks/hero/hero title="Vacancy" img="vacancy/hero-bg" ext="png"}}

<div class="content__wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="container container--small">
      {{>blocks/section-title title="Start your career in a diverse and exciting environment."}}
      <h3 class="news-single__subtitle">
        In our company you will work with the most talented managers, experts and engineers who are passionate about
        their business and the future of aircraft construction. We are driven by passion and share one direction that
        will change the whole world for us and for our future ups and downs.
      </h3>
      <div class="news-single__text-wrapper">
        <p class="news-single__text">We strive to win talented young people for our company! Our extensive training
          programs will provide you with a deep understanding of the aviation industry. Join our strong team and help us
          in our mission to shape the future.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{>blocks/image-with-content
      title="Vision of the company"
      text="Democratized aviation. A future world in which a personal flight and three-dimensional mobility become widely available to all consumers."
    }}

    {{>blocks/image-with-content
      reverse=true
      title="Our goals are to go forward, together with talented people"
      text="Provide freedom, fun and adventure to fly to all who dream about it, creating the most exciting, intuitive, safe and affordable personal aircraft in the world thanks to an unrivaled fusion of design and technology."
    }}

    {{>blocks/image-with-content
      large=true
      title="Your career opportunities in our company"
      text="A team of professionals, people passionate about their business is the key value of the company. Development, attraction of new employees are the priority of the recruitment service."
    }}
  </div>
</div>

